      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَنِ اُبْتُلِيَ بِالْقَضَاءِ فَلاَ يَقْضِيَنَّ وَ هُوَ غَضْبَانُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3234 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Whoever is tested with judging should not pass judgment while he is angry.\""
        ]
      }
